__content\">\n                            <div class=\"cover-image test-cover\" itemscope>\n                                    <a class=\"test-cover-link\" href=\"/book/10.1007/978-3-319-91743-6\">\n        <span class=\"u-screenreader-only\">Learning and Collaboration Technologies. Design, Development and Technological Innovation</span>\n        <img class=\"test-cover-image\" src=\"https://media.springernature.com/w306/springer-static/cover/book/978-3-319-91743-6.jpg\" itemprop=\"image\" alt=\"\"/>\n    </a>\n\n\n\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </aside>\n                    <div class=\"main-body\" data-role=\"NavigationContainer\">\n                        \n\n\n\n                        <article class=\"main-body__content\">\n                            <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"FulltextWrapper\"><div class=\"ArticleHeader main-context\"><div id=\"enumeration\" class=\"enumeration\">    <div>\n        <a data-test=\"ConfSeriesLink\" href=\"/conference/lct\">\n            <span data-test=\"ConfSeriesName\"> International Conference on Learning and Collaboration Technologies</span>\n        </a>\n    </div>\n<p class=\"test-LocationInConferenceProceeding icon--meta-keyline\"><span data-test=\"ConferenceAcronym\">LCT 2018</span>: <span class=\"BookTitle\"><a href=\"/book/10.1007/978-3-319-91743-6\" data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"Book title\" data-track-label=\"\">Learning and Collaboration Technologies. Design, Development and Technological Innovation</a></span><span class=\"page-numbers-info\">\n                pp 136-146</span><span class=\"u-inline-block u-ml-4\"> |\n                <a href=\"#citeas\" data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"Cite as link\" data-track-label=\"Enumeration section\">Cite as</a></span></p></div><div class=\"MainTitleSection\"><h1 class=\"ChapterTitle\" lang=\"en\">From Persona to Living Persona, Preliminary Data from a Pilot Study in HCI Education</h1></div><div class=\"authors u-clearfix\" data-component=\"SpringerLink.Authors\"><ul class=\"u-interface u-inline-list authors__title\" data-role=\"AuthorsNavigation\"><li><span>Authors</span></li><li><a href=\"#authorsandaffiliations\" data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"Authors and affiliations tab\" data-track-label=\"\">Authors and affiliations</a></li></ul><div class=\"authors__list\" data-role=\"AuthorsList\"><ul class=\"test-contributor-names\"><li itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\" class=\"u-mb-2 u-pt-4 u-pb-4\" itemprop=\"author\"><span itemprop=\"name\" class=\"authors__name\">Christophe\u00a0Kolski</span></li><li itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\" class=\"u-mb-2 u-pt-4 u-pb-4\" itemprop=\"author\"><span itemprop=\"name\" class=\"authors__name\">Bruno\u00a0Warin</span><span class=\"author-information\"><span class=\"authors__contact\"><a href=\"mailto:bruno.warin@univ-littoral.fr\" title=\"bruno.warin@univ-littoral.fr\" itemprop=\"email\" data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"Email author\" data-track-label=\"\"><img src=\"/springerlink-static/images/svg/email.svg\" height=\"24\" width=\"24\" alt=\"Email author\" /></a></span></span></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"main-context__container\" data-component=\"SpringerLink.ArticleMetrics\"><div class=\"main-context__column\"><span><span class=\"test-render-category\">Conference paper</span></span><div class=\"article-dates\"><span class=\"article-dates__label\">First Online: </span><span class=\"article-dates__first-online\"><time datetime=\"2018-05-30\">30 May 2018</time></span></div></div><div class=\"main-context__column\">    <ul id=\"book-metrics\" class=\"article-metrics u-sansSerif\">\n            <li class=\"article-metrics__item\">\n                     <span class=\"test-metric-count article-metrics__views\">1.2k</span>\n                     <span class=\"test-metric-name article-metrics__label\">Downloads</span>\n            </li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div><span id=\"test-SeriesTitle\" class=\"vol-info\">\n                Part of the\n                <a class=\"gtm-book-series-link\" href=\"/bookseries/558\">Lecture Notes in Computer Science</a>\n                book series (LNCS, volume 10924)</span></div><section class=\"Abstract\" id=\"Abs1\" tabindex=\"-1\" lang=\"en\"><h2 class=\"Heading\">Abstract</h2><p id=\"Par1\" class=\"Para\">The <em class=\"EmphasisTypeItalic \">Persona</em> technique consists in introducing, in the process of realization of a product (good or service), one or more fictitious personages representing users of the product to be designed. In this paper, we present a preliminary study on the adaptation of the <em class=\"EmphasisTypeItalic \">Persona</em> technique to promote the pedagogical quality of practical works in HCI education. These practical works concern the specification using UML and the sketching of interactive systems. We call the variant used: <em class=\"EmphasisTypeItalic \">Living Persona</em>. The teacher plays the role of the <em class=\"EmphasisTypeItalic \">Persona</em>; this <em class=\"EmphasisTypeItalic \">Persona</em> is described in paper form and provided to each student. The teacher interacts with groups of students (each simulating a company), for a better understanding of the user needs. After recalling the history of the concept of <em class=\"EmphasisTypeItalic \">Persona</em>, we explain how we develop it and introduce it into guidelines of practical works. Then we present a first study with 54 Master\u2019s degree students in Computer Science. We end the paper by presenting the implementation of a more complete study to detect other pedagogical contributions of this promising technique.\n</p></section><div class=\"KeywordGroup\" lang=\"en\"><h2 class=\"Heading\">Keywords</h2><span class=\"Keyword\">Persona\u00a0</span><span class=\"Keyword\">Living persona\u00a0</span><span class=\"Keyword\">Interactive system\u00a0</span><span class=\"Keyword\">Practical work\u00a0</span><span class=\"Keyword\">HCI education\u00a0</span></div><div class=\"note test-pdf-link\" id=\"cobranding-and-download-availability-text\"><div id=\"chapter_no_access_banner\">This is a preview of subscription content, <a id=\"test-login-banner-link\" href=\"/signup-login?previousUrl=https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fchapter%2F10.1007%252F978-3-319-91743-6_10\" data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"Preview banner - Log in\" data-track-label=\"\">log in</a> to check access.</div></div><div class=\"article-actions--inline\" id=\"article-actions--inline\" data-component=\"article-actions--inline\"></div><section class=\"Section1 RenderAsSection1\" id=\"Bib1\" tabindex=\"-1\"><h2 class=\"Heading\">References</h2><div class=\"content\"><ol class=\"BibliographyWrapper\"><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">1.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR1\">Minist\u00e8re de l\u2019enseignement sup\u00e9rieur et de la recherche, Programme P\u00e9dagogique National du Dipl\u00f4me Universitaire de Technologie en informatique, France (2013)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Minist%C3%A8re%20de%20l%E2%80%99enseignement%20sup%C3%A9rieur%20et%20de%20la%20recherche%2C%20Programme%20P%C3%A9dagogique%20National%20du%20Dipl%C3%B4me%20Universitaire%20de%20Technologie%20en%20informatique%2C%20France%20%282013%29\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">2.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR2\">Cole, M.: Using wiki technology to support student engagement: lessons from the trenches. Comput. Educ. <strong class=\"EmphasisTypeBold \">52</strong>, 141\u2013146 (2009)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceDOI\"><a class=\"gtm-referenc